    "name": "SimPlaE",
    "steam_appid": 3150000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;欢迎你，这里是 SimPlaE —— 一台可以模拟多个世界的装置。&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/9ef9dca29739d1822b8377f4217c8419.avif?t=1770627712\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras_big/9ef9dca29739d1822b8377f4217c8419.webp?t=1770627712 width=1560 height=1561 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;现在开始教程。&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>通过模拟来玩平台游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/662e3bad1f30d91d501cc67f2746961c.avif?t=1770627712\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则1</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有角色都会根据特定条件与给定地形互动并自行移动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不能直接操控角色的移动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/f8391bf67deec8d7b7f908a880fbfb51.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/f8391bf67deec8d7b7f908a880fbfb51.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/f8391bf67deec8d7b7f908a880fbfb51.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则2</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong>观察</strong>来了解角色的行为模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将槽位中提供的资源拖放进行<strong>放置</strong>，以设计新的路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4865c929cb2c9f642f3a7eaa62e7d928.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4865c929cb2c9f642f3a7eaa62e7d928.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4865c929cb2c9f642f3a7eaa62e7d928.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必要时请积极利用提示和工具提示，这有助于激发新的想法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/588eef6bafb260d62d516669c4e0caf7.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/588eef6bafb260d62d516669c4e0caf7.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/588eef6bafb260d62d516669c4e0caf7.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则3</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成模拟的方法有很多，但最优解只有一个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SimPlaE 会对你的选择进行评价并给予评级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/14f5482ff3b8d87675484023b8ad5746.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/14f5482ff3b8d87675484023b8ad5746.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/14f5482ff3b8d87675484023b8ad5746.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关关卡，迎接各种难度与机制的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的地形和角色动作正等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4856515a2b2fe31735c14f8145cbe1a6.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4856515a2b2fe31735c14f8145cbe1a6.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/4856515a2b2fe31735c14f8145cbe1a6.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>模拟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SimPlaE 中存在着多种被模拟的横版平台世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟的主角需要你的帮助才能实现他的愿望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/d96723b3ef413a98f9197ade518acdfa.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/d96723b3ef413a98f9197ade518acdfa.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/d96723b3ef413a98f9197ade518acdfa.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟的目的是什么？在模拟的尽头等待你的会是什么结局？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/137aedf59bc4608ff78332c35ff03854.poster.avif?t=1770627712\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/137aedf59bc4608ff78332c35ff03854.webm?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/137aedf59bc4608ff78332c35ff03854.mp4?t=1770627712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">&quot;我们将怀着极大的兴趣观察你的选择。祝你好运。&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试玩版</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版包含 20 个关卡，占正式版内容的 20%。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版将包含 100 个关卡，以及模拟主角所经历的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150000/extras/a48197fb100ed03161dda32dd39c45a2.avif?t=1770627712\" width=1560 height=423 /></span></p>",
